Title: Unlearning - Lesson I
Note: To the memory of Elizabeth Bishop
---
What is the purpose of creation?
That every thing might simply be.
Why does God give, and then take away?
God doesn't. God gives that
every thing might be.
Why create at all, God?
Why?
    Because, that is what I do.
